Plotting Life Expectancy over the Years

library(ggplot2)

ggplot(gapminder_df, 
       aes(x = year, y = lifeExp, group = country, color = continent)) + 
  geom_line() + 
  scale_y_log10() + 
  scale_x_continuous(limits = c(1997, 2007)) + 
  theme_bw()
